{"tid":2450381,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賽馬直播｜ 2021-03-17 競馬Fact Check 快活谷草地夜馬  即場貼士 AI模擬賽果 排隊馬","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T12:42:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21f8c866bf3900e0bbfc7e6d41dc2ad3e3c269f4","tid":2450381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"#賽馬 #直播 #競馬FactCheck<br />\n<br />\n賽馬直播｜<br />\n2021-03-17 競馬Fact Check Live直播九場HKJC香港賽馬會快活谷草地夜馬 <br />\n即場貼士 AI模擬賽果 排隊馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DglOfb7idk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDglOfb7idk0&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=8f3e6cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DglOfb7idk0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.8M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n今晚（17日）跑馬地馬場上演九場賽事，頭場定於傍晚6時45分開跑。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果《競馬Fact Check》屆時直播各場賽事，讓馬迷猶如置身場內睇跑馬。<br />\n<br />\n谷草王方嘉柏近三次谷草均有馬贏，共獲五Ｗ，今次繼續佈下強陣，有望藉「主場」之利再連場數糊。<br />\n<br />\n主持會分析此路人馬各駒機會，配合各場馬匹賽績、體重變化、人馬合作等統計資料，一表睇晒，方便刨馬。<br />\n<br />\n《競馬Fact Check》今季新增AI模擬賽果，集各項data進行運算，識別出哪些是機會馬，以得分高低排序，一目了然！<br />\n<br />\n主持亦會即場解答讀者留言，與讀者互動交流；另外會加插騎練賽前訪問，大家或者從中可以搵到方向。<br />\n<br />\n此外，仲會新增出閘預測走位圖，等觀眾了解今場賽事形勢，邊啲馬可以賺步速；邊啲馬相對蝕底，務求幫大家捉更多冷馬。<br />\n<br />\n《競馬Fact Check》新增參賽馬賠率走勢，由隔晚到即場，一目了然；電腦預計臨場大戶落飛馬，讓馬迷落注前作參考，增添勝算。<br />\n<br />\n《競馬Fact Check》將於傍晚6時10分開播，屆時Youtube及《果燃台》會全程直播。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=8b3dbe3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a>​<br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=fb0bb56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia​</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=4a6e4141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone​</a><br />\nAndroid App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-Android%E2%80%8B&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=cbd7df63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android​</a><br />\n======="},{"pid":"1b6392c720b4c345759abd08ec77ee9681e22d2f","tid":2450381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"第3場"},{"pid":"fc36efc165e34ae3e138a7231379e5ccc757cc18","tid":2450381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T12:14:30.000Z","msg":"第4場"},{"pid":"29485d078f62703a813685f73df0997a172c871e","tid":2450381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"第5場"}]}